desc.1: Data is the new raw material in the corporate world. Are you willing to experiment with that? If not, don't be concerned. Technex is offering an in-depth Data Science program to educate you on the ins and outs of data gathering, storage, analysis, and prediction.
desc.2: Prerequisite : There are no prerequisites for attending this workshop. Anyone interested can participate in this workshop.
